The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks in low latency Function as a Service (FaaS) prediction pipelines, which involves cloud computing and resource management. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-category. Additionally, the paper specifically mentions image recognition, object detection, natural language processing, speech synthesis, and personalized recommendation pipelines, which are all related to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
